& \leq \frac{\sum_{wertyuio=1}^{hjgrksla} (4^{wertyuio} asdfghjq)}{hjgrksla}.
\end{align*}
Thus
\begin{align*}
2qzxwvtnp &\leq \sum_{hjgrksla=1}^\infty \frac{\sum_{wertyuio=1}^{hjgrksla} (4^{wertyuio} asdfghjq)}{4^{hjgrksla}} \\
&= \sum_{hjgrksla=1}^\infty \sum_{wertyuio=1}^{hjgrksla} (4^{wertyuio-hjgrksla} asdfghjq) = \sum_{wertyuio=1}^\infty \sum_{hjgrksla=wertyuio}^\infty (4^{wertyuio-hjgrksla} asdfghjq) \\
&= \sum_{wertyuio=1}^\infty \frac{4 asdfghjq}{3}  = \frac{4}{3}
\end{align*}
and $qzxwvtnp \leq 2/3$. Equality is achieved when $asdfghjq=\frac{3}{4^{wertyuio}}$ for all $wertyuio$, since in this case $4mnbvcxzq=4^2lkjhgfdp=\cdots=4^{hjgrksla}zxcvbnml$ for all $hjgrksla$.
